#. <section class="sutta" id="sn46.44"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.44:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.44:0.2"
msgid "5. Cakkavattivagga"
msgstr "5. A Wheel Turning Monarch"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.44:0.3"
msgid "44. Duppaññasutta"
msgstr "44. Witless"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.100"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.44:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe … ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha … and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn46.44:1.2"
msgid "“‘duppañño eḷamūgo, duppañño eḷamūgo’ti, bhante, vuccati."
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of ‘a witless idiot’."

msgctxt "sn46.44:1.3"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, ‘duppañño eḷamūgo’ti vuccatī”ti?"
msgstr "How is a witless idiot defined?”"

msgctxt "sn46.44:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Sattannaṃ kho, bhikkhu, bojjhaṅgānaṃ abhāvitattā abahulīkatattā ‘duppañño "
"eḷamūgo’ti vuccati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicant, they’re called a witless idiot because they haven’t developed "
"and cultivated the seven awakening factors."

msgctxt "sn46.44:1.5"
msgid "Katamesaṃ sattannaṃ?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "sn46.44:1.6"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgassa … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgassa—"
msgstr ""
"The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, "
"rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity."

msgctxt "sn46.44:1.7"
msgid ""
"imesaṃ kho, bhikkhu, sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ abhāvitattā abahulīkatattā ‘"
"duppañño eḷamūgo’ti vuccatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"They’re called a witless idiot because they haven’t developed and cultivated "
"these seven awakening factors.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.44:1.8"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
